data.description: Completely renovated 3 bed/2 bath home in historic area.  Open floor plan - everything updated in 2021 - new roof, driveway, plumbing, HVAC, hot water tank, toilets, doors, quartz counter tops, appliances, dovetail appliances, lighting, plumbing, LVP flooring, bathrooms, exterior paint & hardware. Interior repainted in 2023. Split bedroom floor plan. Primary bedroom w/luxury bath & HUGE walk in closet. Renovated kitchen w/SS appliances & gas cooking. All of the modern amenities! New shed in back
